ace: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">更新完成后，选择后台右上角的“清除缓存”操作，清除之后，可以去网站首页刷新一下，就可以看到已经成功升级后的博客模版咯。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"># 特殊说明：</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">当前模版里提供的“文章模型”，新增了一些字段（是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本、评分等级等），这是因为我将该模型处理成具备“普通文章和产品下载”的属性，在网站栏目“杂的文（普通文章）、资源下载（产品下载）”里，可以看到这两种不同显示方式的文章详情页。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">也就是说当前模版提供的“文章模型”里，在后台新建文章内容时，会看到有个“是否为模板”的选项，它就是负责在前端文章详情页里判断是否显示为“产品下载”页面的功能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果你需要使用“下载”属性的文章，请在后台的文章内容里补充下图所示的内容信息（是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本、评分等级）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果仅仅是普通文章，就不要去勾选该选项。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text-align: center; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><img src=\"https://www.duoguyu.com/uploads/ueditor/image/20190419/1555637379750544.jpg\" title=\"「多骨鱼博客」Intro v5.2 完整版-附带演示数据，博客模版主题- YzmCMS模版主题，免费下载\" alt=\"「多骨鱼博客」Intro v5.2 完整版-附带演示数据，博客模版主题- YzmCMS模版主题，免费下载\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 680px; width: 680px;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">最后，如果在安装或使用过程中，有任何问题，请在下方留言评论，或在社区里发帖，亦可在QQ群里161208398里寻求帮助。</p><p><br/></p>', '', '', '/images/cover/1561132050443308.jpg', '1', '3', '0', '0', '0', '2', '2', '0', '1', '0', '', '1', 'markbro', '2019-11-23 19:35:10', '2019-12-20 10:20:18', '0', '');
INSERT INTO `cms_resource` VALUES ('2019112319403531361647', 'recommend', '葡萄资讯模板主题，葡萄内容管理系统模板主题', '1', '经过最近一段时间的折腾，终于把个人博客重构了，算是跟过去包括2018年说个还算ok的再见吧。这次是近乎完美的模版主题，因为它本身就直接是从【多骨鱼主站】线上版本pull下来的。', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">经过最近一段时间的折腾，终于把个人博客重构了，算是跟过去包括2018年说个还算ok的再见吧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">之后，经过这么几天时间，下定决心把【多骨鱼主站】的完整前端模版打包分享出来，这次是近乎完美的模版主题，因为它本身就直接是从【多骨鱼主站】线上版本pull下来的。<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">不过，由于之前写了太多小的迭代和升级，以及自定义字段，还有在袁大神的帮助下进行的二次开发。导致不能把整个源码download出来直接使用，而且之前也发布了一个阉割后的版本。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">于是，这次来个小福利吧，或者也叫做共享？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">嘿嘿。经过近两天的整理及优化，移除了自定义字段、函数、二开时候的部分js，在保留和原站几乎一样的界面情况下，整理完善的【多骨鱼】v3.2-完整版-模版主题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">好了，废话少说，上截图。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"># 模版截图(部分) #</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margi