Fang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">更新完成后，选择后台右上角的“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">清除缓存</strong>”操作，清除之后，可以去网站首页刷新一下，就可以看到已经成功升级后的博客模版咯。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"/></p><h4 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\"># 特殊说明：</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">当前模版里提供的“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">文章模型</strong>”，新增了一些字段（<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">、评分等级</strong>等），这是因为我将该模型处理成具备“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">普通文章</strong>和<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">产品下载</strong>”的属性，在网站栏目“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">杂的文（普通文章）、资源下载（产品下载）</strong>”里，可以看到这两种不同显示方式的文章详情页。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">也就是说当前模版（Intro v5.2 完整版）提供的“文章模型”里，在后台新建文章内容时，会看到有个“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">是否为模板</strong>”的选项，它就是负责在前端文章详情页里判断是否显示为“产品下载”页面的功能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果你需要使用“<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">下载</strong>”属性的文章，请在后台的文章内容里补充下图所示的内容信息（<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">是否为模板、压缩包上传、模版类型、CMS版本、评分等级</strong>）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) !important;\">如果仅仅是普通文章，就不要去勾选该选项。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: medium none; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; text-size-adjust: none; color: rgb(69, 69, 69); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Lantinghei SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;HanHei SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, Arial, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, 微软雅黑, STHeiti, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254); text